<?xml version="1.0" encoding="UTF-8"?><song><time_sig>(8.6.8.6.)</time_sig>
<title>Free Salvation by Christ ƲIT36</title>
<lyrics>[V1]
 Ʋba Pi̱ki Chihowa ma!
 Himak a fehna ka,
 Hatak ilbʋsh' im anumpa
 Auet ish haklashke.

[V2]
 2Chiso Chisʋs atukmʋto
 Ilap im issish ʋt
 Nan isht ʋlhpihi̱sa hi ʋt
 Ai a̱hli mak atok.

[V3]
 A yʋmohmi pulla hona,
 Hatak yoshoba mʋt
 Okcha̱ya bʋnna hokmʋno,
 Ish okchalincha he;

[V4]
 Ʋlhpisa tok pulla hona,
 Okcha̱ya pi bʋnna:
 Pit e chim asihi̱lhha ka,
 Auet pi̱ nukha̱kló.

[V5]
 Okcha̱ya hoka pi bʋnnʋt,
 Ik a̱hli, aiahnit
 Pit e chim aiokpahanchi,
 Auet ish haklashke.</lyrics>
<aka>Ʋba Pi̱ki Chihowa ma</aka>
<hymn_number>36</hymn_number>
</song>